etherlabmaster (1.5.2+20180508gitc8d0140-1) stretch; urgency=low

  * added non-generic network driver compiles to dkms
  * switched to git with Gavin Lambert's unofficial patchset,
    enabling non-generic driver builds against official Debian RT
    kernel v. 4.9; see https://github.com/ribalda/ethercat
  * un-hardcoded kernel version in dkms sources so dkms can build native
    drivers for any supported kernel version
  * added patch to mini.c so it can be built for pre-4.18 kernels
  * added kernel version regexes to match native drivers
  * installed /etc/ethercat.conf, wanted by ethercatctl and systemd units
  * added systemd service files

 -- John Morris <john@zultron.com>  Fri, 27 Jul 2018 19:08:17 -0500

